GELU activation function

Source: R/gelu.R
GELU.Rd

GELU activation function

Usage

GELU(x)

Arguments

x

numeric vector

Value

numeric vector

See also

Other Activation Functions: ELU(), PReLU(), ReLU(), SELU(), Swish(), dELU(), dGELU(), dPReLU(), dReLU(), dSELU(), dSwish(), dlReLU(), dsoftplus(), lReLU(), softplus()

Examples


GELU(c(-2, -1, 0, 1, 2))
#> [1] -0.04550026 -0.15865525  0.00000000  0.84134475  1.95449974

# you can use rxode2 as well
r <- rxode2({
  r = GELU(time)
})
